==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whereness
<hw>Where"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or
state of having a place; ubiety; situation; position.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A point hath no dimensions, but only a <qex>whereness</qex>, and
is next to nothing.</q> <rj><qau>Grew.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whereof</ent>⟦br⟧
